===Noun===
'''[[nit]]-[[picking]]'''
# The painstaking process of removing [[nit]]s -- [[lice]] eggs -- from someone's [[hair]].
# By extension, any process of finding or pointing out tiny details or errors, particularly if the pointed-out details seem insignificant or irrelevant to all but the finder.
#:"Of all life's pleasures, I like nitpicking the best." -- [[w:Wally (Dilbert character)|Wally]] in [[w:Dilbert|Dilbert]]

